{"tid":1806573,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖記欲續約C.朗拿度至2023年！那時已38歲","createTime":"2020-01-01T11:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T16:10:05.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7890302c1cea88fa55c0a3902a082a8a48d351aa","tid":1806573,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"意大利媒體稱，祖雲達斯計劃和C.朗拿度續約到2023年，到那時候葡萄牙人將是38歲。<br />\n<br />\n  《拖連奴體育報》稱，這同時是C洛賓人的意願，他認為自己還有很多可以貢獻的，因此希望續約到2023年。在杜拜的頒獎儀式後，C.朗拿度和自己的經理人文迪斯談了這件事，後者向祖記傳遞了這個信息。<br />\n<br />\n  祖記體育總監帕拉蒂奇得知後，也願意與C.朗拿度延長合約，《拖連奴體育報》稱，祖記預計給他一份新的三年合約，另有一年的延長期選擇。<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度目前在祖記的年薪大約是3000萬歐元，祖記方面希望能在春天就完成與他的續約。"},{"pid":"085d94675b4b0c3c3a9b9c92653d0b9044172f20","tid":1806573,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"C洛賓人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281964c6eedf1663687081ebd3ad2cb6b233a262","tid":1806573,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"不如續埋保方"},{"pid":"47b96c3f929669bf9e55e55b3128921bf7a8a5a2","tid":1806573,"uid":121058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"大巴拿：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ee88affed79f37f331b130ae05519c5c169f76","tid":1806573,"uid":37860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"假設真係踢到2023係祖記退休<br />\n咁c 朗係邊隊既名宿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0fb1df0a7cfb79147f8b61ef04c43b8304027d","tid":1806573,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:33:35.000Z","msg":"球壇人瑞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7b8024e521d843e7849f31da7beff1587e93d9","tid":1806573,"uid":3454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote"